reviews.reviewText: I’ve Ticarve gel to clean my car for years especially my work truck. Working in the oil field. The inside of my work truck gets extremely dusty quickly So I always carry this amazing jell to quickly clean up the dust that gathers on the dash door panels and center console of my truck. Not only does it clean, amazingly and keep your car looking brand new, but it has a very nice aroma. reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Works OK - but not for long
reviews.reviewText: This does pick up stuff, but I dont think its alot better than a cloth and vacum. It does not leave residue and smells nice, but you sometimes have to go over things more than once. It does get into crevices you might otherwise miss. But I can tell that after a few uses it will start losing its stickiness. Best to use as a finish cleaning after you have done your best with a rag and vacum.
